00:38:20.160 --> 00:38:23.290
Now I remember in '74,
sitting there agonizing.

00:38:23.290 --> 00:38:25.890
I had 25 to 30 stocks lined up.

00:38:25.890 --> 00:38:28.990
They're all selling between
