00:38:40.000 --> 00:38:44.730
So it's kind of like they say.

00:38:44.730 --> 00:38:47.067
In a bull market--
in a bear market,

00:38:47.067 --> 00:38:48.150
you don't want an analyst.

00:38:48.150 --> 00:38:50.330
In a bill market,
